Adebolu Adejobi, a teenager with cerebral palsy has emerged as the student with the best WASSCE result in his school. He shares with us his challenges, triumphs and motivation. His parents also revealed some of the challenges they faced raising him as well as how proud they feel at his achievement. Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com